        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-10-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-10-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="1121" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1121">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.115/10–149: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">McConaughy</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-10-01">October 1 [<hi rend="italic">2?</hi>], 1949</date>.<lb/>[Received October 2—12:17
                        a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4151. Following message received by Pattison October 2 at 1045 hrs. local time
                    from <hi rend="italic">Flying Independent:</hi>
                </p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“Chinese warship orders we follow him to 30–14 north, 121–55 east. Advise New
                        York and all authorities.”</p>
                    <p>Message from <hi rend="italic">Flying Clipper</hi> 1100 hrs:</p>
                    <p>“Message just received from Chinese warship</p>
                    <pb facs="1152" n="1142" xml:id="pg_1142"/>
                    <p>‘Follow us to latitude 30–14 north, longitude 121–55 east. You must proceed
                        to follow orders by my Government. If not, will fire on you.’</p>
                    <p>Notify immediately American Consulate General, State Department and New
                        York.”</p>
                </quote>
                <p>Please pass CNO.</p>
                <p>Sent Department 4151; repeated Embassy Canton 1143, Hong Kong 290, Taipei
                    333.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">McConaughy</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
